## Getting Started

<h4>Prerequisites</h4>
<ul>
<li>Java Version 11</li>
<li>Node Version 16</li>
<li>MySQL Version 8</li>
</ul>
<h4>Installation</h4>

For Frontend:-

1. cd frontend
2. npm i
3. npm run dev

For Backend:-

1. cd backend
2. mvn clean install
3. mvnw spring-boot:run

